<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-info">
    <h1>Be the best carer for your best friend</h1>

    <div class="hero-action">
      <%= link_to 'Sign up now',  new_user_registration_path, class: "hero-signup-btn" %>
      <br>
      <br>
      <%= link_to 'or login to your account', new_user_session_path, class: "hero-login-btn" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%= link_to root_path do %>
    <button class="icon-up"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up"></i></button>
<% end %>
<div class="our-services">

  <h2>Our services</h2>

  <div class="service-card">
    <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar-check"></i>
    <p><strong>Never forget the medication</strong><p>
    <p>With our medication schedule, you'll never forget to give the medicine to your pet. Enter a few details and we'll nudge you to help remember.</p>
  </div>


  <div class="service-card">
    <i class="fa-regular fa-hospital"></i>
    <p><strong>Talk with vets if needed</strong><p>
    <p>If you have any question about your pet's medication, you can always ask your vet.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="service-card">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-pills"></i>
    <p><strong>Search our Vets</strong><p>
    <p>We have a network of Vets so you can find help for your best friend where ever you are.</p>
  </div>

</div>


<div class="home-find-vets" id="home-find-vets">
  <h2>Find the closest vet</h2>
  <p>ChillPill has associated vets all around the world. Find one near you.</p>
  <div class="home-map"
    data-controller="map"
    data-map-markers-value="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
    data-map-api-key-value="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
   </div>
</div>

<div class="home-witnesses">
  <i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i>

  <h2>Make your pet the happiest<br>pet in the world.</h2>

  <h2>Trusted by <%= User.all.count %> users around the world.</h2>

  <div class="witness-one-img"></div>
  <div class="witness-txt">
    <h3>“It was difficult to organize the medicine intake when you have so many members in the house, Chillpill made it a lot easier”</h3>
    <p>— Maria González</p>
  </div>

  <div class="witness-two-img"></div>
  <div class="witness-txt">
    <h3>“It was difficult to organize the medicine intake when you have so many members in the house, Chillpill made it a lot easier”</h3>
    <p>— Wagon Le</p>
  </div>

</div>
